

---SELENIUM ARCHITECTURE-----



1. selenium standalone server download
2. Keep standalone server and chrome driver.exe in same folder
3. Invoke cmd
4. Reach to that folder path by cd..
5. Type java -jar standalone server.1.1.1.jar
6. Note the localhost:4444
7. Type it in chrome browser and create session
8. check json wire protocol command, API and hands on the POSTMAN

----Postman---
/session/:sessionId----GET
http://localhost:4444/wd/hub/session/76740564bef473a147fa61c63bfddb2e
 
/session/:sessionId/url---POST
http://localhost:4444/wd/hub/session/76740564bef473a147fa61c63bfddb2e/url

Body->Raw->JSON(application/json)
Pass the url as
{
"url":"http://www.google.com"
}



------------Automation Framework Architecture:---------------
 
• POM (Page Object Model) Design Page Factory API of WebDriver 
• Maven (Build Automation Tool) 
• Test Libraries for different UI Pages 
• Test Utilities for different generic functions 
• Report - Dashboard (Pass/Fail Test) by using Extent Report 
• API Jenkins - Continuous Integration Tool 
• GITHub Repo (Code Versioning Tool)
